ingredientsDesc:
Analyser
Operator’s Manual
Application Software
1 connection cable between the PC and the instrument
1 electric power Cord
1 pack of plastic tips (containing 250)
Disk with calibration data

50 35ml.containers for reagents
50 75ml. containers for reagents
100 3.5ml. vials for Standard/Controls

1 waste pipe (2m)
1 I/O IBM card

Used tips container
1 metal needle for micro-volumes
3 containers for wash and buffer solutions
1 removable support for loading reagents
1 removable support for loading samples
1 container for loading disposable tips
